query:
SELECT b.siteId, s.id as sites_id, s.siteNumber
FROM bookings b
LEFT JOIN sites s ON b.siteId = s.id
WHERE b.status = 'confirmed' 
AND b.startDate >= '2025-07-01'
AND s.id IS NULL
LIMIT 10;
